{"tid":37070,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[索尼罪大滔天] 強烈建議巴打們唔好買Sony機","createTime":"2016-12-13T06:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T07:21:08.000Z","uid":42469,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"456b1fa56e6ecf8d8a37e247a649a8bfc8acc2c8","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:16:20.000Z","msg":"原來Sony mobile係無香港分部<br />\nSony HK就係TSO，咁TSO既服務有幾差我都唔洗多講<br />\n我部機保養期內已經整左八次，最後一次比佢地整穿埋防水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八次搭車排隊夾埋浪費左我超過30個鐘<br />\n最後一次TSO counter叫佢換機馬上黑臉淨係講無咁既服務<br />\n叫佢搵大佬跟就話自己就係大佬<br />\n<br />\n屌佢一send信上Sony Global就換得機，個TSO真係on撚鳩無柒用<br />\n點知原來Sony Global只係redirect我封信去TSO投訴部<br />\n問佢點解啲員工完全唔肯幫我，佢就話會跟進改善，有問題可以打黎<br />\n屌你老母我睇勻成間TSO我都見唔到有投訴部電話<br />\n<br />\n同佢講我要延長埋保養就reject我，淨係肯換機<br />\n機我就會照換，訴我會繼續投<br />\n已經決定send上去Sony CEO個email到<br />\nKazuo.Hirai@jp.sony.com<br />\nSony機好唔好講唔出，但Sony係香港既售後我敢講就屎都不如<br />\n<br />\n講咁多都係想勸各位巴打<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚買Sony啊!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱先開錯係吹水台，而家開返係手機台<br />\n巴打們唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca68b5f9dfa9d37eafa1c3b3baae06a1b7528b4","tid":37070,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:16:39.000Z","msg":"下部想換sony<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6825e511c2d0812487f8a7f1481af1c05646e7c2","tid":37070,"uid":44933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:17:01.000Z","msg":"屌你咩以為你講相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4a1ab0989cbe652515a77eab3cb539649311e4","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下部想換sony<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTSO每維修一次都會為你加入新問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你好彩買中部唔洗整既我諗都無事嘅"},{"pid":"bde4085c6b5824411127faeaa1da7a000d1006ad","tid":37070,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下部想換sony<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTSO每維修一次都會為你加入新問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你好彩買中部唔洗整既我諗都無事嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd34e264b65e6e923b9878fae47be472404f0808","tid":37070,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />部分同意既<br />\n但sony 機真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：用左3部sony"},{"pid":"f74192b3b97723e4eae5b60d3cde2eebcdf6f89f","tid":37070,"uid":2090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:37:45.000Z","msg":"年零前sony 係cwb 仲有個維修部 係真係sony 自己既維修部<br />\n個時d服務真係好好.依家比哂tso做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55affde84d32af196460a1f66d821235df0e65e6","tid":37070,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"Android 手機牌ndq,第一垃圾係三星，第二就係Sony"},{"pid":"9db7eaaebd4e8e0dfc21289162897c2e4fe85ee1","tid":37070,"uid":64780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你咩以為你講相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsony d 相機好屈機, 我覺得仲好過canon nikon"},{"pid":"46b81906166b9c575547bfa3b93aec362e900adf","tid":37070,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"an機最好服務聽講話得htc,不過又吹到高價廢spec<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9683fcf10ebad1ab05a9d59dbc24b7bc948e64d9","tid":37070,"uid":62299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"sony機水貨自己整仲方便<br />\n自己換芒換板好簡單，sony機算易拆"},{"pid":"2e885efde80f964e1b53d037e764bac800c71cc9","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />部分同意既<br />\n但sony 機真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：用左3部sony</blockquote><br />\n我幾乎用左十年Sony，都叫得做半個打手<br />\n今時今日都係折墮到要post篇咁既文勸人咪買<br />\n值唔值得為靚搏命，自己諗啦，我就不了<br />\n<br />\n從狗升格為人，就在此刻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2efa140a976723f230a71eba12e736e1dca935","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"呢篇文我會長推，救濟世人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87185ef54249013d6e2517bafc6df260115efae7","tid":37070,"uid":7547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"做過間垃圾公司嘅part time<br />\n狗也不屌"},{"pid":"9f50d9c239c2fe85a0c89ca8458c53820c2566c7","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做過間垃圾公司嘅part time<br />\n狗也不屌</blockquote><br />\ndetail plx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a