同跌極都冇事</blockquote><br />\n有事起黎你就大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTSO只會越整越衰，最後你機都無得用<br />\n<br />\n我部機壞過moon, touch, proximity sensor, mic, 而家爛緊 nfc 同 touch<br />\n<br />\n每一樣都係TSO幫我加落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358ea24e3034d80c497f82241d64e2761bc54129","tid":37070,"uid":46026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:32:04.000Z","msg":"推，淨係用過z3，不過用左一個月唔啱用放左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769bfed979722f262ba780156714a7a867b6babb","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:56:52.000Z","msg":"Told you everything loud and clear, but nobody's listening~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb95c3dbbcba9fd31fbbd6e3314498aa36e3fa5","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:07:10.000Z","msg":"十連先<br />\n1"},{"pid":"cd0dea9fa04b370ff7806094ece107cef78858bf","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"2c5737dbcd61bc726473c04d164f2084ac4e7f0b","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"245e1a221ce24ff74ecddc4f3abf67447488100c","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:08:32.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"04b779786d6df6c063d113d4de9948e045876be9","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:08:52.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"01bab5f62582d073af4e5fb0afd2b1741378e165","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"226f0d328f39ac91ff0f522395f526ec79e144cf","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:09:15.000