 />"},{"pid":"188e2914f8f996cd352d7ed3f306732f38f784f9","tid":37070,"uid":7547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做過間垃圾公司嘅part time<br />\n狗也不屌</blockquote><br />\n想寫落寄比CEO既信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCEO 未必管依啲<br />\n<br />\n因為都幾耐以前，親耳聽到啲full time/manager 同啲客講：<br />\n4G 依家多左人用，速度同3G 差唔多<br />\n<br />\nsony 專門做sensor ，800萬像素靚過其他牌子1300萬<br />\n<br />\n玻璃機身散熱好過金屬<br />\n<br />\n其他牌子好易爆mon，sony 任跌都好少爆<br />\n等等之類<br />\n<br />\n你可以留意下，sony 機啲sales 特別中意踩其他牌子，總之自己賣唔到就攬炒<br />\n<br />\n行政上啲仆街野就唔講喇"},{"pid":"654d19d6411919c71c07f965ea911c1f3a1044ac","tid":37070,"uid":20990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:54:06.000Z","msg":"本身下部想換Sony<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fee574cb30db0031d5187569c97993410744d0","tid":37070,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:11:23.000Z","msg":"Dell又係咁，Asus又係咁，係香港個個品牌既售後都當啲客係狗咁撚<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌，做香港人真係好撚折墮啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Sony用家們，你只係狗黎咋</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc59bb26282b80383e11fdbc191